<item>
 <title>Я Русь свою любил и холил...</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/blog/ya-rus-svoyu-lyubil-i-holil</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://vse.la/images/blogi_images/getimage_10_-_kopiya.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://vse.la/images/styles/thumb330/public/blogi_images/getimage_10_-_kopiya.jpg&quot; width=&quot;330&quot; height=&quot;248&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Я Русь свою любил и холил,&lt;br /&gt;
И в том признаться не стыжусь,&lt;br /&gt;
И в той душевной дикой боли,&lt;br /&gt;
Я лил в лугах без меры грусть,&lt;br /&gt;
Но сидя молча на пригорке,&lt;br /&gt;
Внимал я чуду дивных мест,&lt;br /&gt;
Вдыхал полыни запах горький&lt;br /&gt;
И воскресал, целуя крест.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Автор: Виктор Шамонин-Версенев&lt;br /&gt;
Читает: Александр Водяной&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-rubrika field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Рубрика:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/blog/tvorchestvo&quot;&gt;Творчество&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Теги:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/shamonin&quot;&gt;шамонин&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/stihi&quot;&gt;стихи&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/skazki&quot;&gt;сказки&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/audio&quot;&gt;аудио&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/peyzazhnaya&quot;&gt;пейзажная&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/blog&quot;&gt;блог&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/vodyanoy&quot;&gt;водяной&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/rus&quot;&gt;русь&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/teg/krest&quot;&gt;крест&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
